* Make CImg use CoreGraphics to convert image data, removing the need for libjpeg, libpng, etc.
* Instead of having to specify paths, make it accept NSImage instances.
* Create standalone build by building static libs of the dependencies.
* Create podspec that does not expect dependencies to be installed through homebrew.
* Release first stable version.

Later:

* Make compatible with iOS.
* Support audio and video hashing.
